--------------------------
 Testing Tips

Create Test Mode keys in Razorpay Dashboard.

Use test card e.g. 4111 1111 1111 1111, any future expiry, any CVV, any OTP.

Verify your server logs for /verify-payment and webhooks.

Keep a DB table like payments with fields: order_id, payment_id, amount, currency, status, signature_valid, metadata.
